<h2 id="IgU6gn"><strong>The Wheel of Time and Sanderson’s ascension</strong></h2>
<p id="qlWry2"><a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/interview-how-brandon-sanderson-ended-the-wheel-of-time/"><em>Mistborn </em>caught the attention of Harriet McDougal</a>, wife of Robert Jordan, who died in 2007 without finishing his epic series <a href="https://www.polygon.com/23860119/wheel-time-season-2-preview-tease-new-episodes">The Wheel of Time</a><em>. </em>He’d asked McDougal to find someone to complete his work and she chose Sanderson for the job. The release of <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Gathering-Storm-Book-Twelve-Wheel/dp/0765341530?tag=polygon05-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank" has-subtag="true" data-cdata='{"rewritten_url":"https://www.amazon.com/Gathering-Storm-Book-Twelve-Wheel/dp/0765341530?ascsubtag=___pl__p_23873180__m_m-placeholder__s_s-placeholder__t_w__c_c-placeholder__r_r-placeholder__d_d-placeholder\u0026tag=polygon05-20","subtag_max_length":99,"subtag_delim_length":3,"subtag_key":"ascsubtag","subtag_data":{"ascsubtag":"___pl__p_23873180__m_m-placeholder__s_s-placeholder__t_w__c_c-placeholder__r_r-placeholder__d_d-placeholder","tag":"polygon05-20"},"encode_subtag":false}'><em>The Gathering Storm</em></a>, the first of three books Sanderson wrote based on Jordan’s notes for how the series would end, propelled him to the New York Times bestseller list.</p>
  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25354563/Gathering_Storm.jpg">
      
