<p id="dHKxUa"></p>
<h2 id="5OifoD"><strong>The ‘secret projects’</strong></h2>
<p id="e60eIk">Unable to go on book tours, attend conventions, or do any other type of traveling during the COVID-19 lockdowns, Sanderson did what he does best and wrote four more books. He turned to Kickstarter in 2022 to fund their publication and raised nearly $42 million. The campaign remains the site’s most successful campaign of all time.</p>
